## So here problem is tell we are inserting React and ReactDOM code thorugh networks calls in our codebase and babel also through network calls and you knwo these calls are very expensive so tell me is our code ready to ship into production and why do we need bundler ?

## Answer --> No our codebase is not ready to ship into production let me tell you why assume we have deployed our code on server our html,css,react file,reactDom file full files of whole code i am talking about,babel full file i have pushed on to the server and now our user has requested the application so server par toh load vese hee badh gya because html,css,js files toh thi + react,reactDOM,babel ka pura source code rakha hua server cost badha + user ne request kri html file aayi abh html parser jese jese files dekhga request maarega css file ko , fhir abh react reactDOm babel ke liye network request jayegi pura source code aayega abh js ko call jayegi js file me hum react reactDOm yah babel ka pura code toh use kar nahi rhe kuch hee part usse krre hai toh user ka data jyada lgega + application storage jyada legi browser me + slow chlega application + net jyada use hoga so yeh bahut galat hai hamara app production ready nahi tha toh usko productiion ready krne ke liye kuch asa kr skte hai react,reactDOM,babel ko network cal nah kre internet bachega application jaldi render hogi server cost kam hogi browser me app kam space lega + kuch asa ho jo jo react reactDOM babel ka jo jo part use krre hai woh hee deploye kre production par ek aa mechanism chahiye jo pure codebase ko minified , compressed,optimize,faltu ke variables ko hata de so yeh sab kaam manually krenge toh development par dhyaan nahi de paayege so iske liye ek mechanism hai jisko bundler bolte hai.


## Now we have understood why do we even need the bundler bundler kya kya kaam karta hai and there are diffrent types of bundler exist in the market like vite,parcel,create-react-app,webpack and many more but vite is dominating all the other bundlers so we are going to study bundler in this course.

## So lets get react,reactDOM,babel,vite into our project manually vese ek command me sab khud hojata hai lekin lets do manually first of all npm int kro NPM->it works as node package manager ek repositry hai jisme js ki saari libraries ka code hai vaha se laana pdega humko through commands usse pehle npm init kro woh ek package,json file install krega which manages all the library which our project needs and unke approx version hamara app ka version,start krne ki command,test krne ki command,production build krne ki command,entry point of the app yeh sab rakhta hai packge.json.

## Dependancy : dependancies ar the libraries which our application needs like react,reactDOM,.babel yeh sab depandancy hai but vite is devDepandancy the diffrence between them is normal depandancy production me hoti hai jese react reactDOM ka code but vite ka kaam hai hamaro faster dev experince dena building ke time par + dev build deta hai faster + code ko inified compressed optimization commens remove krke html css js and dependies ko bundle krke ek dev build deta hai during the development time but production me iska kuch kaam nahi hota .

## Package-lock.json: It is a files jo jo transitive depandancy hai depandancy chianing un sbke exact version lock krke rakhta hai unke baare me information rakhta hai. 